            "row_content": "<p><br/>No. Frequency Circle is built on behavioral reinforcement, nervous system regulation, and structured repetition. There’s no blind belief required. The system focuses on daily alignment practices that stabilize identity and reduce cognitive drift — not mystical shortcuts.</p>",
            "page": ""
