          "settings": {
            "heading": "How quickly will I see results?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Most members report internal shifts (clarity, emotional stability, reduced overthinking) within the first 2–3 weeks.<br/><br/>External results depend on consistency. This is a discipline-based system — not a one-night transformation.</p>",
